  14:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****                         ##### FLASH peripheral features #####
  15:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****   ==============================================================================
  16:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****            
  17:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****   [..] The Flash memory interface manages CPU AHB I-Code and D-Code accesses 
  18:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****        to the Flash memory. It implements the erase and program Flash memory operations 
  19:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****        and the read and write protection mechanisms.
  20:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       
  21:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****   [..] The Flash memory interface accelerates code execution with a system of instruction
  22:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****        prefetch and cache lines. 
  23:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c **** 
  24:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****   [..] The FLASH main features are:
  25:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) Flash memory read operations
  26:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) Flash memory program/erase operations
  27:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) Read / write protections
  28:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) Prefetch on I-Code
  29:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) 64 cache lines of 128 bits on I-Code
  30:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       (+) 8 cache lines of 128 bits on D-Code
