  37:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       memory of all STM32F4xx devices.
  38:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****     
  39:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       (#) FLASH Memory IO Programming functions: 
  40:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Lock and Unlock the FLASH interface using HAL_FLASH_Unlock() and 
  41:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****                 HAL_FLASH_Lock() functions
  42:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Program functions: byte, half word, word and double word
  43:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) There Two modes of programming :
  44:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****             (+++) Polling mode using HAL_FLASH_Program() function
  45:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****             (+++) Interrupt mode using HAL_FLASH_Program_IT() function
  46:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****     
  47:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       (#) Interrupts and flags management functions : 
  48:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Handle FLASH interrupts by calling HAL_FLASH_IRQHandler()
  49:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Wait for last FLASH operation according to its status
  50:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****            (++) Get error flag status by calling HAL_SetErrorCode()          
  51:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c **** 
  52:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****     [..] 
  53:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       In addition to these functions, this driver includes a set of macros allowing
  54:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****       to handle the following operations:
  55:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****        (+) Set the latency
  56:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****        (+) Enable/Disable the prefetch buffer
  57:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****        (+) Enable/Disable the Instruction cache and the Data cache
  58:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****        (+) Reset the Instruction cache and the Data cache
  59:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****        (+) Enable/Disable the FLASH interrupts
  60:./STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash.c ****        (+) Monitor the FLASH flags status
